org.datavec.api.transform.reduce.geo

Class CoordinatesReduction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.transform.reduce.geo.CoordinatesReduction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, ColumnOp, AggregableColumnReduction

    public class CoordinatesReduction
extends java.lang.Object
implements AggregableColumnReduction
    Applies a ReduceOp to a column of coordinates, for each component independently. Basically a dispatchop with n = 2 an integrated coordinate parsing & serialization
